<paragraph id="726EE90F7CC82E081728A6D48D3F6F6F" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">Spornlos</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="E2EC16D8D26764C39C3DB879EFB3B0C8" pageId="null" pageNumber="617" type="description">
<paragraph id="D7D50B56F8A21388F13ACA1F7434BFF0" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">
Gattung 
<emphasis id="4F2B0A43275171930750A5DD4032A35E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">mit nur 1 Art.</emphasis>
Die Gattungsmerkmale sind in der Artdiagnose enthalten. 
<emphasis id="6CC15B1B76F5DB811C9A5EB11070D174" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">
Die Lippe von 
<taxonomicName id="B6219FCC3CF88CDC904E71EDF6754F74" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Aceras" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="617" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Aceras</taxonomicName>
bildet keinen Sporn; einziges Unterscheidungsmerkmal von jenen Arten der Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="9804A5EB8555BD39B02A9DD30357DD56" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Orchis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="617" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Orchis</taxonomicName>
, bei denen die 
<normalizedToken id="C28F895433DA179C74FB905593B49E5C" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A4BE3947A486E71D53312F54D202166C" originalValue="helmförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">helmfoermig</normalizedToken>
zusammengeneigt sind.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="329DB37D57B6FFF31BE161C9CD7C848E" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">
<emphasis id="2D4A92B85421605F69AAEFA035569B11" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="617">
Die Gattungen 
<taxonomicName id="56DDE0D06DD7C1293C5A4452610C5637" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Aceras" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="617" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Aceras</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="579E76448EC7D19B354A9E70CFE53A70" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Orchis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="617" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Orchis</taxonomicName>
bilden Bastarde
</emphasis>
(siehe unter Gattungsbastarden).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
